  Kernel::HasOnPositiveSide_3  


A model for this must provide:
 

    
         
    bool  

         
          
             
    fo.operator() (     
      Kernel::Plane_3  h,  Kernel::Point_3  p)     
                
    returns true iff  p  lies on the positive side of  h  
( h  is considered a halfspace).
                 
         
    bool  

         
          
             
    fo.operator() (     
      Kernel::Sphere_3  s,  Kernel::Point_3  p)     
                
    returns true iff  p  lies on the positive side of  s .
                 
         
    bool  

         
          
             
    fo.operator() (     
      Kernel::Tetrahedron_3  t,  Kernel::Point_3  p)     
                
    returns true iff  p  lies on the positive side of  t .
            

  Refines  AdaptableFunctor  (with two arguments)
 

  See Also   CGAL::Plane_3 &lt; Kernel &gt;    CGAL::Sphere_3 &lt; Kernel &gt;    CGAL::Tetrahedron_3 &lt; Kernel &gt;   

